{"tid":1968300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄: 會向學校推薦狄志遠的「SOSo Mask」以每個3蚊賣俾各小學 估預第一批可售110萬個","createTime":"2020-04-11T14:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T16:27:42.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"932f3da74591b32f9e339355e78f9e7c9cc3d17b","tid":1968300,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">教育局局長楊潤雄昨表示，局方早前向學界引薦新思維創黨主席、家庭教育學院總監狄志遠的「SOSo Mask」團隊，為全港資助小學供應中童口罩。狄志遠表示，預計在5月之內向近300間小學提供首批110萬個口罩，每個售價3元，強調只是收回成本，「睇唔到有咩利潤」。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「SOSo Mask」2月底曾發新聞稿，表示訂購的5台口罩機已經安裝完成，首月的生產量為30萬個，預計翌月的產量可提升至70萬個，亦已簽妥訂購可製作1,200萬個口罩材料的合約，部份已經付運。團隊當時表示口罩部份會免費派發給個別行業前線員工、獨居長者，以及醫療輔助隊等，其餘會以每個2元向診所、醫護人員、非牟利機構和基層市民發售。<br />\n<br />\n狄志遠接受《蘋果》查詢時解釋，每個2元的售價是要以籌款補貼，惟後來捐款用盡，加上材料越來越貴；為可長時間供應口罩，決定將售價調升為每個3元，以收回材料和人手等成本。狄強調，是以社企模式營運，「開車送貨都係朋友義工去做」以減低成本，又指家庭教育學院一向不是做生產，只是「邊行邊學」。<br />\n<br />\n教育局發言人回應稱，早前收到小學學界反映在採購兒童口罩時遇到極大困難，局方遂致力提供協助，聯繫學校議會和本港生產兒童口罩的機構，讓雙方直接洽商。發言人稱，教育局沒有參與雙方往後的合作討論，學校在運用政府津貼購置物料時，須按照既定採購指引及程序。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200410/WIA6QOUUP6IAS2HXWBDN4FIC4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200410%2FWIA6QOUUP6IAS2HXWBDN4FIC4I%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=431bacaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200410%2FWIA6QOUUP6IAS2HXWBDN4FIC4I%2F&h=9dd417eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200410/WIA6QOUUP6IAS2HXWBDN4FIC4I/</a>"},{"pid":"cb113c80bed85dbb07131f1762cbd81585721120","tid":1968300,"uid":16846,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"又貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9ec37b723dada43efc712414fb348c474c3d21","tid":1968300,"uid":263618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"屌擺到明利益輸送"},{"pid":"3a8a7de105f3f3b37d753dfddaa4cbfbca257779","tid":1968300,"uid":24788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:38:20.000Z","msg":"2蚊個就差唔多"},{"pid":"6160b056051fbcaa309c3b27a6b05fdce0dc6e26","tid":1968300,"uid":162362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:41:38.000Z","msg":"鄧家彪明明話成本係HK0.2一個"},{"pid":"29729a5c79ff13a70a6cfddab8bfb5692b5554d2","tid":1968300,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f9ec37b723dada43efc712414fb348c474c3d21","tid":1968300,"uid":263618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"屌擺到明利益輸送"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:00:36.000Z","msg":"正常應該要投標"},{"pid":"da7b49d2d4d7e3b79d0e5ba4c8df3387f5bcbf11","tid":1968300,"uid":36702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"icac : 我地訓緊教呀  訓左十幾年架喇  唔好嘈醒我"},{"pid":"70a346f3e7ae3a86b840f7b403505eb99c7af5c0","tid":1968300,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da7b49d2d4d7e3b79d0e5ba4c8df3387f5bcbf11","tid":1968300,"uid":36702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"icac : 我地訓緊教呀  訓左十幾年架喇  唔好嘈醒我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"無icac一年慳到幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e510623be8f1e004db18dc998fde49bb2fa4d5de","tid":1968300,"uid":15084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70a346f3e7ae3a86b840f7b403505eb99c7af5c0","tid":1968300,"uid":168389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da7b49d2d4d7e3b79d0e5ba4c8df3387f5bcbf11","tid":1968300,"uid":36702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11